{"tid":1667863,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"TVB廣告商戰線，大家勤力一點洗板","createTime":"2019-10-21T16:34:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-21T17:29:57.000Z","uid":171506,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"bef7187a59613212389245f88a412bd9bb3ba3d6","tid":1667863,"uid":171506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T16:34:06.000Z","msg":"零風險和理非行動，小學生都幫到手，得番百幾人真係鄧推post巴打慘。"},{"pid":"2af2a40d7db74308195898470d2fff1cdccfdb35","tid":1667863,"uid":171506,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T16:38:07.000Z","msg":"我覺得呢個行動有實際作用，廣告真係跌緊，政府無連儂牆，電視台係主力宣傳工具。"},{"pid":"7138c5bfea349d9c3f4590267f6c1395d660dee7","tid":1667863,"uid":53612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T16:42:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9bc860524f023950fcb7946af8b2612909d81fe2","tid":1667863,"uid":171506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T16:49:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.aastocks.com/tc/stocks/news/aafn-con/NOW.971294/latest-news\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.aastocks.com%2Ftc%2Fstocks%2Fnews%2Faafn-con%2FNOW.971294%2Flatest-news&d=bp2T%2F%2B5c5q8hcpZmRI3qNpriIWEbfV0cuvPRs67P9cA%3D&h=99ac58c0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.aastocks.com/tc/stocks/news/aafn-con/NOW.971294/latest-news</a>"},{"pid":"d80dabb8e7adb59139d38d5cb164729c1b0d22cf","tid":1667863,"uid":171506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T16:52:06.000Z","msg":"2019/10/21 09:04<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n據《信報》報道，電視廣播(<a href=\"http://00511.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F00511.HK&d=bp2T%2F%2B5c5q8hcpZmRI3qNpriIWEbfV0cuvPRs67P9cA%3D&h=ed77b52a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">00511.HK</a>)近日向廣告商發出新一份廣告價目表，有別於過往每年加價3%-5%，翡翠台、J2及無線財經資訊台明年廣告費將維持不變，另外更下調客戶入場門檻，過往客戶至少承諾投放與去年廣告費100%或以上才可獲最優惠的廣告套餐，惟現時承諾水平降至90%即可，另外公司亦提供額外10%的下調空間，即是倘客戶未能完成投放水平，降至81%亦可接受，是沙士以來首度跌穿100%。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以最多優惠的套餐計算，計及所有折扣後明年變相減價4%-7.4%，加上公司同時推出大量優惠，如廣告投入亨800萬元可獲廣告時段首格或最後一格播出，而65秒以上較長的廣告將有額外30%折扣。"},{"pid":"cc0d27a62efd316d69afb883ed2e10b417c6f900","tid":1667863,"uid":156767,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T16:58:34.000Z","msg":"Follow A餐雞蛋撞石牆"},{"pid":"93d6ec70389f65ff98774c5023cab085d9e4c930","tid":1667863,"uid":268123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T17:29:57.000Z","msg":"【香城施政報告2019】群策群力 轉危為機<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1656908\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1656908</a><br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>政治問題</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 重塑公民身分戶口政策保障國家、香港安全和利益<br />\n- 取消18區區議會、建立地域市政議會<br />\n- 禁止公務人員在任前、任內和任後獲港外榮典<br />\n- 改善高鐵一地兩檢操作方式<br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>便民基建</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 修正港鐵、巴士可加可減機制<br />\n- 完善機場集體運輸並加強機場、港珠澳大橋協同發展<br />\n- 興建東鐵、西鐵快速線並完善輕鐵和西鐵聯乘關係<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V1VCzpw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV1VCzpw.jpg&h=7b29ce56&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RYt8F4w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRYt8F4w.jpg&h=eecde813&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>醫療、教育方向</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 以減少送院為目標的社區護理服務<br />\n- 重塑教育, 著重知識、技能層次分工<br />\n- 興建至少四所新區域全科醫院<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B2D8F34.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB2D8F34.png&h=cb82275f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n求正評及幫推！"}]}